  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Family Autism Center at The Arc of South Norfolk provides supports and services to people diagnosed with autism spectrum disorders and their families.  We provide respite care, specialized recreational programming, training for family members and provide information and referral sources to families looking for assistance.  Autism impacts 1 in every 68 children- we have seen an increase of 100 additional people requesting our services in the last 12 months alone- we serve 652 people currently</narrative>
